Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 在偷拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太安静了 反而睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用你的摄魂机…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个时间留住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪陪我?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我把杯子都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光注意些蘩文缛节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想轻松征战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个过分的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我恶作剧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管外面是下雨或下雪都把我关在家门外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连吃晚饭的时候都不开门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也算是替一直忙于工作的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格管教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 其实我知道一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在不被人发现的状态下 从后面的窗户进去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还守着这个秘密 这话只跟你说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10加普就靠岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是把罗巴带来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在赞巴尼号上是它自己做出的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎幺说呢 我在想见到他们时该用什么表情才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经很出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…刚才是在夸我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你离别半年的故乡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是尖端岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里打的电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…尖端岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在姐姐在军队的宿舍里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我估计春也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我可以跟她联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个电话之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 姐姐肯定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打算在这里停泊三天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用担心你的划艇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去惹宪兵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为北方政府的进犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上的军方警戒变的更加严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要到处乱跑比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我只是在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你办件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 二号目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风向变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西南方向 顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正 三号目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对我这么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分数不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过反应值偶尔会极其低下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会集中精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也认为多愁善感是年轻人的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很担心寺岡古市的情况吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况在新兵中也很常见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心想着出成果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等放下心的时候 心情就会一落千丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别让我失望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹给你打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保准吓你一跳 超超超大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…他回来了 回尖端岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉他姐姐在宿舍以后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说让我打电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我们家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 到演武广场去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那里谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指竹原明之吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严密警戒他自己的住宅 竹原龙藏的诊所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及有可能与他接触的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西村春怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着不管就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实之种因孤独而心碎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 开始沉闷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 旁边一盆 没开花的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是休诊日吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那样…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 请进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候应该说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我回来了” 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之回到岛上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在大概去见龙藏医生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之的朋友来我们家告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感觉有些不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的名字非常好听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐总算到了 娜琪亚美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你认识她吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拯救的那个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有石化 现在仍然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…你说过的吧 会让他平安的回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早点把他带回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绿先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是姐姐你叫我来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话 快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想呆在明之的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之对我而言 永远都是无可替代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 擅自把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你母亲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想算是…不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 好歹把房间打扫一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么脏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这已经算是比较整洁的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡 要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问这回你又在研究什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这座岛上也不怎么太平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那右臂 是校车爆炸时受的伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 类似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是个有才能的“庸医” 你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着父母的事情只有初恋就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 看起来虽然挺那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希洛克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你见个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我救了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能用一两句话就解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她还留有一点思考能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请装做没看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我能原谅这位卉孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我能这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿在你身上的希洛克想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也只是在寻求答案的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受到了指引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉…大家都想成为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹原明之有可能已经潜伏在里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里待机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现对象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即要求各配置点增援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是竹原龙藏医生吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有一些有关令郎的问题要问…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你也能喜欢我家的橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打扰你休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我的腰就是不争气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 阿兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来急诊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纱特制健康双层便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待您再次惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得明之回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最近她不知怎么回事 一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她一直就只顾看着前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能拜托的人只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这一点还真像春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的一直是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队里的事没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已经被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭时回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时报告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未确认到对象回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其母亲也未有异常举动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒位置变更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置 对象就读的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水里有铁锈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…回答呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这孩子老是爱恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训斥他的时候倒是装出一副再也不犯了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天却又想出别的什么鬼点子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只好把他关在门外禁止吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还对邻居们说 “只要发现他往家里钻 就揍他”什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从诊所后山潜入厨房的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当我想“他差不多该求饶了吧”而准备放他进来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在道歉的时候 脸上沾了好多饭粒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到厨房一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子的晚饭…居然少一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时已经消了气 非常惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 喜欢恶作剧也要有个限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们为这孩子的行踪 忙得焦头烂额的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他却悄悄的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我给你打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定过一阵子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹这点 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是他母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉因为一些事情想见你却见不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发型很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么回来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又想来见我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你的话 我就必须向上面报告你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你来见我的话 我是按耐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我又不想把你交给军方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是无可救药的想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于不知道自己想要什么的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能得到那些东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有你所没有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是12厘米的身高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:20:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的东西 这家伙全都得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拥有的东西都是我渴望得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 我就是那12厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的希洛克和憎恨产生了共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希洛克?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他是扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤都破了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得一分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直在努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日以继夜 孜孜不倦地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事一点意义都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果才是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否被选中才是关键 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 现在心情好像很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于千疮百孔 成痴成狂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于相隔千里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的时刻即将到来

